w swirlspines to get one to materialize) This would eliminate the contention and bottleneck. Then make Phinny drop at least one epic piece each time. <br>
<br>
What's the result?  The epic quests were supposed to have you killing an epic level mob. By the time we reach 59 and 60 Phinny is no longer a real challenge other than the waiting and the contention. The epic should be at least doable by a level 50 (the spell is useable at 46?) and for a GROUP of level 50-ish (very low 50s) folks this would be a fun fight and a challenging one.<br>
<br>
For the higher level folks it means you would go down with a few friends (you'd NEED more friends cause you'd have to kill all guardians and MIGHT have to kill swirlspines to GET Guardians). So let's see... lower level folks get a fun and challenging fight and higher levels get to go in, get their stuff, and leave so teh NEXT round of folks can come in.<br>
